{
  "stem": "1641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he-- he came to the hospital, to my place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had in all of the rooms, I had a little-- not I, but the hospital-- had a little oven, which was mostly used to cook the dinner for the SS men.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this little oven, it-- it was, you know, with wood-- we had wood, which we could burn there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anyhow, and so he brought the potatoes, and I made the fire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then we had 20 minutes in between where we could make boiled potatoes, or we could just half-boil them, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It wasn't quite raw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So-- so he gave me four potatoes to eat, and he had the other four.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And maybe he had four more sometimes, which he took back to his friend to the-- his-- and then he had to rush away.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And thanks, Frank, I'll-- see if I can bring you some tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he told me another story, which [? will end ?] of some interest, how they got potatoes in his block sometimes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Some-- there was a-- there was a deal that the people who had to go to get the so-called coffee, which was just black-- black water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It wasn't coffee, but it was-- it looked like coffee, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was black, hot water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they rushed to the kitchen every morning to get a barrel full with this hot water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And on some days, the deal was that the-- the man in the kitchen, he put in five kilograms of potatoes on the bottom of the coffee.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He filled it up in the coffee and in-- in exchange to get-- to get some gold teeth.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Somebody had to sacrifice his gold teeth, so give him two gold teeth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And for that, he got the potatoes in the coffee.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
